lines: dpal ldan rigs brgya'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
gang 'dul sgyu 'phrul dra bar mngon bzhengs te
srid dang zhi ba'i dge legs 'dod rgyu'i char
'bebs mdzad bshes gnyen tshogs rnams phyag gi yul
zab rgyas dam chos skye ba lnga pa'i dbyangs
thar 'dod rna ba'i dpyid du rtag snyan pas
bdag rgyud rmongs pa'i gnyid mun rab bsal te
legs lam snang bar spyod 'di bla ma'i drin
dman la lhag par brtse ba'i phyag yangs kyis
srid pa nyam nga'i gcong rong zab mo las
'dzin mdzad dge ba'i bshes kyi bka' drin tshad
gzugs su grub na nam mkha' snod du chung
thub gsung ma dros mtsho chen las 'ongs pa'i
gnyis med ye shes rgyu dngos ci rigs kyis
rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung lam 'bras bu la
mchog gi blo ldan rang gir spyod pa'i gnyen
dbang gi bla ma rnams la gus phyag 'tshal
rigs brgya'i khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang
rje btsun rdo rje rnal 'byor ma
paN chen a b+ha ya ka ra
paN chen dpe med srung ba
rje btsun tsong kha pa chen po
mkhas grub dge legs dpal bzang po
ba so chos kyi rgyal mtshan
mkhas btsun yon tan rgya mtsho
thar lo lugs kyi ring brgyud ni
'jam gsar ba man gong ltar la
de nas nyeg po chos ldan
go lung pa gzhon nu dpal
thar lo nyi ma rgyal mtshan
bu ston rin po che man 'dra
bka' 'gyur ba dpal ldan bzang po
yongs 'dzin gling sprul rdo rje 'chang
7yang na dpal ldan bzang po
sgo mang khang gsar rin po che
mnga' ris pa shes rab rgyal mtshan
phu chung pa gzhon nu rgyal mtshan
ka ma pa 'brom rin chen rgyal mtshan
zhang ston dar ma rgyal mtshan
stabs ka pa 'brom byang chub bzang po
ston pa nam mkha' rin chen
gshin rje mthar byed gdong drug pa'i rjes gnang
bgegs mthar byed nag po phyag gnyis pa'i rjes gnang
hUM mdzad nag po phyag gnyis pa'i rjes gnang
stobs po che dmar po phyag bzhi pa'i rjes gnang
dam tshig gsum bkod gtso rkyang bcas
bcu gsum pa dbang sdud skor la
ku ru ku l+le gsang sgrub
dpa' mo snying gi gser thig
mkhyen brtse'i chu 'dzin dkrigs pa'i klong yangs nas
zab rgyas gdams ngag bdud rtsi'i gru char 'bum
bdag blo dad pa'i zhing sar rtag 'bebs pa'i
bshes gnyen rnams kyi bka' drin 'dir yang dran
gsung rab kun gyi snying po bsdu bsdu ba
tshul 'di thun reton dang nyan pas kyang
dam chos 'chad dang thos pa'i phan yon tshogs
rlabs chen sdud par nges pas de don bsam
